BurnaBoy tweets days after his escorts were detained for allegedly firing gunshots in a club in Lagos



Recall that few days ago, a report of Birna Boy’s escort shooting a married man surfaced online. According to the report, BurnaBoy was making passes at a married woman in the club.



Her husband got infuriated and challenged the singer. Things took a different turn when the singer’s orderly identified as Inspector Ibrahim allegedly fired a gunshot at two persons who are currently hospitalised.
































